25
00:21:22,490 --> 00:21:23,813
PLEASE?

26
00:21:26,690 --> 00:21:27,921
SURE.

27
00:21:29,383 --> 00:21:30,583
LIKE BEFORE?

28
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:35,461
