30
00:21:45,325 --> 00:21:46,689
YEAH.

31
00:21:51,788 --> 00:21:53,656
YOU SHOULD LET IT GO.

32
00:21:55,013 --> 00:21:56,845
TRUST ME,
LIFE'S TOO SHORT.

33
00:21:57,601 --> 00:21:59,861
BESIDES,
NO ONE EVER LOST ANY SLEEP

34
