AND IT DOES.

51
00:22:55,021 --> 00:22:56,864
I DON'T LIKE
THIS WORLD, KEITH.

52
00:22:57,755 --> 00:22:58,929
I CAN'T BE HERE.

53
00:23:08,388 --> 00:23:10,055
