OUT OF BOTH OF US --

95
00:25:11,811 --> 00:25:15,196
ALL CURLY HAIR
AND VENOM.

96
00:25:18,370 --> 00:25:20,251
AND YOU TOLD HER
THAT HER ART MATTERED,

97
00:25:20,578 --> 00:25:22,278
AND SHE NEEDED THAT.

98
00:25:22,312 --> 00:25:24,078
SHE NEEDED
THE QUIET SATISFACTION

99
00:25:24,111 --> 00:25:26,010
OF KNOWING THAT SOMEONE
BELIEVED IN HER.

100
00:25:26,994 --> 00:25:27,911
I DID BELIEVE IN HER.

101
00:25:28,389 --> 00:25:30,377
YEAH, BUT YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO SAY IT.

102
00:25:30,793 --> 00:25:33,825
