SEND HER SKETCHES TO THUD.

103
00:25:33,826 --> 00:25:36,026
BUT YOU DID.

104
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:38,020
AND BECAUSE OF THAT,
PEYTON'S A BETTER PERSON.

105
00:25:40,236 --> 00:25:43,293
YOU KNOW, LUKE,
IT'S AN EASY THING --

106
00:25:44,403 --> 00:25:46,189
SAYING "I LOVE YOU"
TO PEOPLE WHO MATTER.

107
00:25:46,777 --> 00:25:48,658
