THAT YOU'RE STILL HERE WITH ME.

126
00:26:56,511 --> 00:27:01,377
* FOREVER AND EVER, AMEN 

127
00:27:03,743 --> 00:27:07,944
* FOREVER AND EVER 

128
00:27:07,977 --> 00:27:11,844
* AMEN 

