LITTLE BROTHER.

176
00:29:25,446 --> 00:29:26,979
I FORGIVE YOU.

177
00:29:31,046 --> 00:29:32,579
GUARD!

178
00:29:32,613 --> 00:29:34,713
BUT HELL WON'T.

179
00:29:34,746 --> 00:29:36,313
[ SCREAMS ]

180
00:29:44,513 --> 00:29:47,146
Clarence:
 STRANGE, ISN'T IT?

181
