 EACH MAN'S LIFE TOUCHES
 SO MANY OTHER LIVES.

182
00:29:50,513 --> 00:29:52,046
 WHEN HE ISN'T AROUND,

183
00:29:52,079 --> 00:29:53,613
 HE LEAVES AN AWFUL HOLE,
 DOESN'T HE?

184
00:29:53,646 --> 00:29:55,246
George: I'VE HEARD
 OF THINGS LIKE THIS.

185
00:29:55,279 --> 00:29:57,313
 YOU'VE GOT ME IN SOME KIND
 OF A SPELL OR SOMETHING.

186
00:29:57,346 --> 00:29:59,346
 WELL, I'M GONNA GET OUT OF IT.
 I'LL GET OUT OF IT.

187
00:29:59,379 --> 00:30:01,079
 AND I KNOW HOW, TOO.

188
00:30:01,112 --> 00:30:02,446
 THE LAST MAN I TALKED TO

189
00:30:02,479 --> 00:30:04,212
 BEFORE ALL THIS STUFF
