200
00:30:48,246 --> 00:30:51,246
AND IT'S NOT LIKE
WE CAN LEAVE HER WITH RACHEL.

201
00:30:52,329 --> 00:30:54,599
BESIDES, YOU'RE REALLY GOOD
FOR HER.

202
00:30:55,713 --> 00:30:58,224
AND I'M NOT SURE SHE CAN
FIND HER WAY WITUT YOU.

