00:32:19,012 --> 00:32:20,876
PLEASE.

222
00:32:22,046 --> 00:32:24,012
DON'T TAKE HER FROM ME.

223
00:32:25,979 --> 00:32:28,154
DON'T TAKE OUR CHILD FROM HER.

224
00:32:32,379 --> 00:32:35,635
It's okay, Nathan.
Just breathe.

225
00:32:36,246 --> 00:32:38,150
It's gonna be okay.

226
00:32:41,212 --> 00:32:42,546
[ DOOR OPENS ]

227
00:32:42,579 --> 00:32:44,012
NATHAN.

228
00:32:50,146 --> 00:32:52,346
[ SNIFFLES ]

